  <brief_title>Cardiovascular Protective Effect of Spironolactone in Hemodialysis</brief_title>
  <official_title>Protective Mechanisms of Aldosterone Antagonists and Their Effects on Cardiovascular Damage in Chronic Renal Failure: Clinical and Experimental Studies</official_title>
  <sponsors>
